IRS990.MissionDesc: The Mission of the Pennsylvania Association of Student Councils is to offer year round opportunities to develop and apply leadership like skills and civic engagement for middle level and high school level students and their advisors throughout Pennsylvania. The Association will accomplish it's mission by disseminating information for building effective organization recognizing individual and school achievements promoting community service and providing enthusiastic forums for networking and sharing ideas and partnering with state organizations that perpeturate civic engagement.
